u003csection\u003e\u003cp\u003eSign up to our newsletter for style and decor inspiration, house makeovers, project advice and more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘If you want something a bit more versatile, you can make a homemade citrus spray. Just boil the peels in water for 10 to 15 minutes, let it cool, strain out the solids, and then pour the liquid into a spray bottle. This can be spritzed around your home wherever you’ve noticed pests, acting as a gentle, chemical-free deterrent.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘For something a little stronger, especially in outdoor settings, try combining the orange peels with cloves. The mix of aromas is particularly off-putting to insects and works well on patios or during outdoor meals.’\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"section-is-this-an-effective-method\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIs this an effective method?\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TojvTDkaS2YwC8fszLmjwE-1920-80.png.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TojvTDkaS2YwC8fszLmjwE-1600-80.png.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TojvTDkaS2YwC8fszLmjwE-1280-80.png.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TojvTDkaS2YwC8fszLmjwE-1024-80.png.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TojvTDkaS2YwC8fszLmjwE-768-80.png.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TojvTDkaS2YwC8fszLmjwE-415-80.png.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TojvTDkaS2YwC8fszLmjwE-360-80.png.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TojvTDkaS2YwC8fszLmjwE-320-80.png.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TojvTDkaS2YwC8fszLmjwE.png\" alt=\"Close-up of common fly on a peice of wood.\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TojvTDkaS2YwC8fszLmjwE-1920-80.png 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.n